articles.title: Finalists dominate leading run-scorers, wicket-takers at U19 World Cup - ICC Cricket
articles.description: Finalists Australia and India dominate the top 10 lists for batters and bowlers, while the Pakistan skipper leads the way for wicket-keepers.
articles.content: Saharan and Musheer were two of four India players to finish inside the top 10, with compatriots Sachin Dhas (303 runs) and Adarsh Singh (238) joining their teammates near the top of the batting list… [+235 chars]
